question: Laura is required to submit a 272-page assignment. She already finished writing 1/16 of the assignment. How many pages does she have left to write?
answer:
Laura has already written 1/16 of the assignment which is 272 pages*1/16 = <<272*1/16=17>>17 pages.
So, she still needs to write 272 pages - 17 pages = <<272-17=255>>255 pages.
#### 255
